{"storyMeta":{"storyReviewType":"NONE","storyId":"act18d0_level_act18d0_st02","storyGroup":"act18d0","storySort":14,"storyDependence":"act18d0_level_act18d0_08_end","storyCanShow":1,"storyCode":"WD-ST-2","storyName":"异乡来客","storyPic":null,"storyInfo":"艾利奥特在萨尔贡度过了漫长光阴，时至今日，他再次来到了凯尔希的面前，命运对他开了一个玩笑，尽管他身边的人都说，命运无法捉摸。","storyCanEnter":1,"storyTxt":"activities/act18d0/level_act18d0_st02","avgTag":"幕间","unLockType":"STAGE_CLEAR","costItemType":"NONE","costItemId":null,"costItemCount":0,"stageCount":1,"requiredStages":[{"stageId":"act18d0_st02","minState":"PLAYED","maxState":"COMPLETE"}],"prev":12,"characters":["黑市商人","艾利奥特","老伊辛","“沙卒”","慑砂","异客","凯尔希","亚叶"]},"lines":[{"type":"header","key":"title_test","skippable":"true","mode":"BLACK_MASK","text":"纯剧情2","id":0},{"type":"stopmusic","id":1},{"type":"dialog","id":2},{"type":"delay","time":"1","id":3},{"type":"blocker","a":"1","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"1","block":"true","id":4},{"type":"background","image":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/d/d9/Avg_bg_bg_srgmarket.png","screenadapt":"coverall","id":5},{"type":"blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"1","block":"true","id":6},{"type":"playmusic","intro":"$drift_intro","key":"https://static.prts.wiki/music/music/act9d0d0/m_avg_drift_loop.mp3","volume":"0.4","id":7,"musicid":0},{"type":"dialogue","name":"黑市商人","text":"喂，都看过来，我们来了个新苦力！你，别发呆了，滚过去。","id":8},{"type":"dialog","id":9},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_171_1","fadetime":"1","block":"true","id":10},{"type":"delay","time":"1","id":11},{"type":"dialogue","name":"艾利奥特","text":"......我是新来的工匠学徒，我叫艾——","id":12,"figure":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/f/f7/Avg_avg_npc_171_1.png"},{"type":"dialog","id":13},{"type":"character","id":14},{"type":"dialogue","name":"黑市商人","text":"好了，闲话少说，都动起来！","id":15},{"type":"dialogue","name":"黑市商人","text":"喂，你，还有你们，随便使唤他。他可是哥伦比亚的高学历分子，比你儿子还年轻！","id":16},{"type":"dialogue","name":"黑市商人","text":"反正他背后没人，和那些被卖来的奴隶差不太多，别弄死了就行。","id":17},{"type":"dialogue","name":"黑市商人","text":"准备工作到死，小学徒。","id":18},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_171_1","id":19},{"type":"dialogue","name":"艾利奥特","text":"......好的。","id":20,"figure":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/f/f7/Avg_avg_npc_171_1.png"},{"type":"dialog","id":21},{"type":"character","id":22},{"type":"blocker","a":"1","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"1.2","block":"true","id":23},{"type":"background","image":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/4/4b/Avg_bg_bg_indoor4.png","screenadapt":"coverall","id":24},{"type":"blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"1.2","block":"true","id":25},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_171_1#6","id":26},{"type":"dialogue","name":"艾利奥特","text":"......伊辛，看！","id":27,"figure":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/e/e6/Avg_avg_npc_171_6.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_173","name2":"avg_npc_171_1#6","focus":"1","id":28},{"type":"dialogue","name":"老伊辛","text":"噢......令人惊奇，这是你用偷来的钢材焊接的？它就像一尊艺术品......","id":29,"figure":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/1/19/Avg_avg_npc_173.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_173","name2":"avg_npc_171_1#3","focus":"2","id":30},{"type":"dialogue","name":"艾利奥特","text":"别说这么肉麻的话，只是个好看些的消耗品。","id":31,"figure":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/3/3e/Avg_avg_npc_171_3.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_173","name2":"avg_npc_171_1#3","focus":"1","id":32},{"type":"dialogue","name":"老伊辛","text":"但你该休息了，你骨折的臂膀刚刚恢复......","id":33,"figure":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/1/19/Avg_avg_npc_173.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_173","name2":"avg_npc_171_1#6","focus":"2","id":34},{"type":"dialogue","name":"艾利奥特","text":"没关系。","id":35,"figure":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/e/e6/Avg_avg_npc_171_6.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"艾利奥特","text":"你知道哪里可以搞到精炼源石吗？","id":36,"figure":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/e/e6/Avg_avg_npc_171_6.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_173","name2":"avg_npc_171_1#6","focus":"1","id":37},{"type":"dialogue","name":"老伊辛","text":"沁礁黑市没有赤金解决不了的事情。","id":38,"figure":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/1/19/Avg_avg_npc_173.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_173","name2":"avg_npc_171_1#6","focus":"2","id":39},{"type":"dialogue","name":"艾利奥特","text":"......那让我们拭目以待。","id":40,"figure":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/e/e6/Avg_avg_npc_171_6.png"},{"type":"dialog","id":41},{"type":"character","id":42},{"type":"blocker","a":"1","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"2","block":"true","id":43},{"type":"background","image":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/d/d9/Avg_bg_bg_srgmarket.png","screenadapt":"coverall","id":44},{"type":"blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"2","block":"true","id":45},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_172_1","id":46},{"type":"dialogue","name":"艾利奥特","text":"......漆黑的蝎子死了。","id":47,"figure":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/9/96/Avg_avg_npc_172_1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"艾利奥特","text":"我们做得很好，不是吗？","id":48,"figure":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/9/96/Avg_avg_npc_172_1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_173","name2":"avg_npc_172_1","focus":"1","id":49},{"type":"dialogue","name":"老伊辛","text":"今天......老伊辛听那个走私贡品的小贩说，“沙卒”是新一任的沁礁之主。","id":50,"figure":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/1/19/Avg_avg_npc_173.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"老伊辛","text":"你认为你是吗？艾利奥特？","id":51,"figure":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/1/19/Avg_avg_npc_173.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_173","name2":"avg_npc_172_1#6","focus":"2","id":52},{"type":"dialogue","name":"艾利奥特","text":"......你希望我是吗？伊辛？","id":53,"figure":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/b/b5/Avg_avg_npc_172_6.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_173","name2":"avg_npc_172_1","focus":"2","id":54},{"type":"dialogue","name":"艾利奥特","text":"我不是个忘恩负义的人，你是我的长辈，这十多年来，我靠你才能活下来。","id":55,"figure":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/9/96/Avg_avg_npc_172_1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_173","name2":"avg_npc_172_1","focus":"1","id":56},{"type":"dialogue","name":"老伊辛","text":"现在你不需要老伊辛了......","id":57,"figure":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/1/19/Avg_avg_npc_173.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_173","name2":"avg_npc_172_1","focus":"2","id":58},{"type":"dialogue","name":"艾利奥特","text":"不......也不能这么说，我们的关系很微妙。","id":59,"figure":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/9/96/Avg_avg_npc_172_1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"艾利奥特","text":"要抱怨的话，就去向那个神神秘秘的女人抱怨吧。","id":60,"figure":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/9/96/Avg_avg_npc_172_1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_173","name2":"avg_npc_172_1","focus":"1","id":61},{"type":"dialogue","name":"老伊辛","text":"......凯尔希......","id":62,"figure":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/1/19/Avg_avg_npc_173.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_173","name2":"avg_npc_172_1","focus":"2","id":63},{"type":"dialogue","name":"艾利奥特","text":"你还记得她的名字，这些年，你越来越不清醒了，我以为你会忘记很多事情。","id":64,"figure":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/9/96/Avg_avg_npc_172_1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_173","name2":"avg_npc_172_1","focus":"1","id":65},{"type":"dialogue","name":"老伊辛","text":"你找过她吗？","id":66,"figure":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/1/19/Avg_avg_npc_173.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_173","name2":"avg_npc_172_1#6","focus":"2","id":67},{"type":"dialogue","name":"艾利奥特","text":"找过。徒劳无功，我最优秀的情报员也没法在哥伦比亚找到一丁点她的情报，何况那家雇佣兵公司在那之后立刻就倒闭了。","id":68,"figure":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/b/b5/Avg_avg_npc_172_6.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"艾利奥特","text":"研究所也被军方控制，一切资料都被销毁，我甚至找不到任何一个参与者......哥伦比亚把他们藏得很好。","id":69,"figure":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/b/b5/Avg_avg_npc_172_6.png"},{"type":"dialog","id":70},{"type":"character","id":71},{"type":"blocker","a":"1","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"3","block":"true","id":72},{"type":"background","image":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/4/4b/Avg_bg_bg_indoor4.png","screenadapt":"coverall","id":73},{"type":"blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"3","block":"true","id":74},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_172_1","fadetime":"1","block":"true","id":75},{"type":"delay","time":"1","id":76},{"type":"dialogue","name":"“沙卒”","text":"伊巴特王酋会在下周途经赤角小镇，呵，多么幽默的命运。","id":77,"figure":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/9/96/Avg_avg_npc_172_1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"“沙卒”","text":"这是一个大好机会——老伊辛，你睡着了吗？","id":78,"figure":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/9/96/Avg_avg_npc_172_1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_173","name2":"avg_npc_172_1","focus":"1","id":79},{"type":"dialogue","name":"老伊辛","text":"......","id":80,"figure":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/1/19/Avg_avg_npc_173.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"老伊辛","text":"老伊辛做了一个梦......","id":81,"figure":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/1/19/Avg_avg_npc_173.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_173","name2":"avg_npc_172_1","focus":"2","id":82},{"type":"dialogue","name":"“沙卒”","text":"又是你的梦。","id":83,"figure":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/9/96/Avg_avg_npc_172_1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_173","name2":"avg_npc_172_1","focus":"1","id":84},{"type":"dialogue","name":"老伊辛","text":"还是那个梦......那个怯薛的脚步踏过冻土与草原，最终来到黄沙之地的梦......","id":85,"figure":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/1/19/Avg_avg_npc_173.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"老伊辛","text":"但这一次，梦稍有不同......","id":86,"figure":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/1/19/Avg_avg_npc_173.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"老伊辛","text":"那是帕夏未曾和老伊辛描述过的场景......我看见一个人......她很像......那个凯尔希......她的另一个姿态......","id":87,"figure":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/1/19/Avg_avg_npc_173.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_173","name2":"avg_npc_172_1","focus":"2","id":88},{"type":"dialogue","name":"“沙卒”","text":"唔。","id":89,"figure":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/9/96/Avg_avg_npc_172_1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_173","name2":"avg_npc_172_1","focus":"1","id":90},{"type":"dialogue","name":"老伊辛","text":"她在。","id":91,"figure":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/1/19/Avg_avg_npc_173.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"老伊辛","text":"当千百年前怯薛的远征粉碎了旧时代的时候，她就在那儿......","id":92,"figure":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/1/19/Avg_avg_npc_173.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_173","name2":"avg_npc_172_1","focus":"2","id":93},{"type":"dialogue","name":"“沙卒”","text":"梦说明不了什么。没有任何法术能越过时间窥伺命运，这是你自己说的。","id":94,"figure":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/9/96/Avg_avg_npc_172_1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_173","name2":"avg_npc_172_1","focus":"1","id":95},{"type":"dialogue","name":"老伊辛","text":"......是的，这只是老伊辛的一个梦......一个没有意义的梦......凯尔希女士不可能和他们有关......但这是否寓意了什么？","id":96,"figure":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/1/19/Avg_avg_npc_173.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"老伊辛","text":"最后，老伊辛还是梦见了他的帕夏。","id":97,"figure":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/1/19/Avg_avg_npc_173.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_173","name2":"avg_npc_172_1#6","focus":"2","id":98},{"type":"dialogue","name":"“沙卒”","text":"哦，这次你的主人又对你说了什么？老忠臣？","id":99,"figure":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/b/b5/Avg_avg_npc_172_6.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_173","name2":"avg_npc_172_1#6","focus":"1","id":100},{"type":"dialogue","name":"老伊辛","text":"他......","id":101,"figure":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/1/19/Avg_avg_npc_173.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"老伊辛","text":"他在梦里......告诉了老伊辛......萨尔贡的方向......","id":102,"figure":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/1/19/Avg_avg_npc_173.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"老伊辛","text":"......","id":103,"figure":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/1/19/Avg_avg_npc_173.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"老伊辛","text":"你打算伏击王酋的队伍。","id":104,"figure":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/1/19/Avg_avg_npc_173.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_173","name2":"avg_npc_172_1#3","focus":"2","id":105},{"type":"dialogue","name":"“沙卒”","text":"是的。","id":106,"figure":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/f/f2/Avg_avg_npc_172_3.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_173","name2":"avg_npc_172_1#5","focus":"2","id":107},{"type":"dialogue","name":"“沙卒”","text":"还是说，你这位曾经的萨尔贡贵族宠臣，要阻止我对一位王酋的大不敬？","id":108,"figure":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/f/f8/Avg_avg_npc_172_5.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_173","name2":"avg_npc_172_1#5","focus":"1","id":109},{"type":"dialogue","name":"老伊辛","text":"——不敬？","id":110,"figure":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/1/19/Avg_avg_npc_173.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_173","name2":"avg_npc_172_1#6","focus":"2","id":111},{"type":"dialogue","name":"“沙卒”","text":"唔。","id":112,"figure":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/b/b5/Avg_avg_npc_172_6.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_173","name2":"avg_npc_172_1#6","focus":"1","id":113},{"type":"dialogue","name":"老伊辛","text":"他们腐朽，无能，只知道无意义地伤害血亲，将无辜的萨尔贡人卷入争斗......","id":114,"figure":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/1/19/Avg_avg_npc_173.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"老伊辛","text":"他们踩踏着沁礁的土地，却干着最低劣的勾当，老伊辛怎会对这种人......表示敬意？","id":115,"figure":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/1/19/Avg_avg_npc_173.png"},{"type":"camerashake","duration":"0.5","xstrength":"15","ystrength":"15","vibrato":"20","randomness":"70","fadeout":"true","block":"false","id":116},{"type":"dialogue","name":"老伊辛","text":"老伊辛要他们偿还代价，老伊辛想要萨尔贡恢复昔日荣光，而非由这些酒囊饭袋来达成！","id":117,"figure":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/1/19/Avg_avg_npc_173.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"老伊辛","text":"老伊辛......对了......老伊辛应当去寻找那座黄金之城！","id":118,"figure":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/1/19/Avg_avg_npc_173.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_173","name2":"avg_npc_172_1","focus":"2","id":119},{"type":"dialogue","name":"“沙卒”","text":"很少看你这么激动，冷静些——","id":120,"figure":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/9/96/Avg_avg_npc_172_1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_173","name2":"avg_npc_172_1","focus":"1","id":121},{"type":"dialogue","name":"老伊辛","text":"......是时候了。","id":122,"figure":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/1/19/Avg_avg_npc_173.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"老伊辛","text":"去吧，孩子，去点一把火，去完成你的复仇。","id":123,"figure":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/1/19/Avg_avg_npc_173.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"老伊辛","text":"等到风定沙落，等到那座永恒之城从风沙中显露面貌......老伊辛要等到那个时候，要找到那里......","id":124,"figure":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/1/19/Avg_avg_npc_173.png"},{"type":"stopmusic","fadetime":"2","id":125},{"type":"dialog","id":126},{"type":"character","id":127},{"type":"blocker","a":"1","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"3","block":"true","id":128},{"type":"background","image":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/5/5a/Avg_bg_bg_corridor.png","screenadapt":"coverall","id":129},{"type":"blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"3","block":"true","id":130},{"type":"playmusic","intro":"$warm_intro","key":"https://static.prts.wiki/music/music/act9d0d0/m_avg_warm_loop.mp3","volume":"0.4","id":131,"musicid":1},{"type":"character","name":"char_379_sesa_1","id":132},{"type":"dialogue","name":"慑砂","text":"......就是这儿了。","id":133,"figure":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/8/88/Avg_char_379_sesa_1.png"},{"type":"dialog","id":134},{"type":"playsound","key":"$d_gen_walk_n","volume":"0.6","id":135},{"type":"character","name":"char_472_pasngr_n_1","fadetime":"1","block":"true","id":136},{"type":"delay","time":"1","id":137},{"type":"dialogue","name":"异客","text":"好。","id":138,"figure":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/d/d7/Avg_char_472_pasngr_n_1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"char_472_pasngr_n_1","name2":"char_379_sesa_1#2","focus":"2","id":139},{"type":"dialogue","name":"慑砂","text":"提醒你，先敲门。","id":140,"figure":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/d/df/Avg_char_379_sesa_2.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"慑砂","text":"别打什么歪主意，精英干员前辈们没一个是吃素的。","id":141,"figure":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/d/df/Avg_char_379_sesa_2.png"},{"type":"character","name":"char_472_pasngr_n_1","name2":"char_379_sesa_1#6","focus":"2","id":142},{"type":"dialogue","name":"慑砂","text":"走吧。","id":143,"figure":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/d/de/Avg_char_379_sesa_6.png"},{"type":"character","name":"char_472_pasngr_n_1","name2":"char_379_sesa_1#6","focus":"1","id":144},{"type":"dialogue","name":"异客","text":"......","id":145,"figure":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/d/d7/Avg_char_472_pasngr_n_1.png"},{"type":"playsound","key":"$doorknockquite","volume":"0.6","id":146},{"type":"dialog","id":147},{"type":"character","id":148},{"type":"blocker","a":"1","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"1","block":"true","id":149},{"type":"background","image":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/0/0d/Avg_bg_bg_infirmary.png","screenadapt":"coverall","id":150},{"type":"blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"1","block":"true","id":151},{"type":"playsound","key":"$dooropenquite","volume":"0.6","id":152},{"type":"character","name":"char_003_kalts_1","fadetime":"1","block":"true","id":153},{"type":"delay","time":"1","id":154},{"type":"dialogue","name":"凯尔希","text":"......","id":155,"figure":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/d/d3/Avg_char_003_kalts_1.png"},{"type":"playsound","key":"$d_gen_walk_n","volume":"0.6","id":156},{"type":"dialog","id":157},{"type":"character","name":"char_003_kalts_1","name2":"char_472_pasngr_n_1","focus":"2","id":158},{"type":"dialogue","name":"异客","text":"......","id":159,"figure":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/d/d7/Avg_char_472_pasngr_n_1.png"},{"type":"delay","time":"0.4","id":160},{"type":"character","name":"char_003_kalts_1","name2":"char_472_pasngr_n_1","focus":"1","id":161},{"type":"dialogue","name":"凯尔希","text":"看来，那枚金币确实送到了你的手上。","id":162,"figure":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/d/d3/Avg_char_003_kalts_1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"凯尔希","text":"老伊辛还好吗？","id":163,"figure":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/d/d3/Avg_char_003_kalts_1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"char_003_kalts_1","name2":"char_472_pasngr_n_1","focus":"2","id":164},{"type":"dialogue","name":"异客","text":"......他消失在了黄沙之中，在三年前某个月明星稀的晚上。","id":165,"figure":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/d/d7/Avg_char_472_pasngr_n_1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"异客","text":"时间。时间连他那样的萨弗拉都能磨灭，我险些以为他也是诸多神话和阴谋中所论述的那种怪异的古老者。","id":166,"figure":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/d/d7/Avg_char_472_pasngr_n_1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"异客","text":"而时间也把我变成了如今这副嘴脸。这副我过去深恶痛绝的嘴脸。","id":167,"figure":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/d/d7/Avg_char_472_pasngr_n_1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"异客","text":"您呢，凯尔希？","id":168,"figure":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/d/d7/Avg_char_472_pasngr_n_1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"异客","text":"您看您......几乎毫无变化。","id":169,"figure":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/d/d7/Avg_char_472_pasngr_n_1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"char_003_kalts_1","name2":"char_472_pasngr_n_1","focus":"1","id":170},{"type":"dialogue","name":"凯尔希","text":"你还是那个“沙卒”吗？","id":171,"figure":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/d/d3/Avg_char_003_kalts_1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"char_003_kalts_1","name2":"char_472_pasngr_n_1","focus":"2","id":172},{"type":"dialogue","name":"异客","text":"我入职时就说过，那都过去了，我有了新的名字。","id":173,"figure":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/d/d7/Avg_char_472_pasngr_n_1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"char_003_kalts_1","name2":"char_472_pasngr_n_1","focus":"1","id":174},{"type":"dialogue","name":"凯尔希","text":"......你骗得了自己，也骗不了我。","id":175,"figure":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/d/d3/Avg_char_003_kalts_1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"char_003_kalts_1","name2":"char_472_pasngr_n_1","focus":"2","id":176},{"type":"dialogue","name":"异客","text":"也许吧，您始终都觉得您是对的。不幸的是，您确实言中许多。","id":177,"figure":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/d/d7/Avg_char_472_pasngr_n_1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"char_003_kalts_1","name2":"char_472_pasngr_n_1","focus":"1","id":178},{"type":"dialogue","name":"凯尔希","text":"你的记性一直不差，艾利奥特。","id":179,"figure":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/d/d3/Avg_char_003_kalts_1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"char_003_kalts_1","name2":"char_472_pasngr_n_1","focus":"2","id":180},{"type":"dialogue","name":"异客","text":"......别拿那个名字叫我。这些包含秘密的代号不正是为此存在的吗？","id":181,"figure":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/d/d7/Avg_char_472_pasngr_n_1.png"},{"type":"dialog","id":182},{"type":"playsound","key":"$rungeneral","volume":"0.6","id":183},{"type":"character","name":"char_345_folnic_1","fadetime":"1","block":"true","id":184},{"type":"delay","time":"1","id":185},{"type":"dialogue","name":"亚叶","text":"老师——啊，抱歉。您有客人？","id":186,"figure":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/7/7f/Avg_char_345_folnic_1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"char_345_folnic_1","name2":"char_003_kalts_1","focus":"2","id":187},{"type":"dialogue","name":"凯尔希","text":"无妨。","id":188,"figure":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/d/d3/Avg_char_003_kalts_1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"char_345_folnic_1","name2":"char_472_pasngr_n_1","focus":"2","id":189},{"type":"dialogue","name":"异客","text":"请便吧。","id":190,"figure":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/d/d7/Avg_char_472_pasngr_n_1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"char_345_folnic_1","name2":"char_472_pasngr_n_1","focus":"1","id":191},{"type":"camerashake","duration":"0.3","xstrength":"15","ystrength":"15","vibrato":"20","randomness":"70","fadeout":"true","block":"false","id":192},{"type":"dialogue","name":"亚叶","text":"......好......","id":193,"figure":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/7/7f/Avg_char_345_folnic_1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"char_345_folnic_1","name2":"char_003_kalts_1","focus":"1","id":194},{"type":"dialogue","name":"亚叶","text":"维多利亚办事处的信使送来了一个包裹，很特别，不是寄给罗德岛，而是寄给您的，后勤部扫描检查过了，里面是一个信息存储设备。","id":195,"figure":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/7/7f/Avg_char_345_folnic_1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"亚叶","text":"寄信人是......海蒂·汤姆森。您认识这个人吗？","id":196,"figure":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/7/7f/Avg_char_345_folnic_1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"char_345_folnic_1","name2":"char_003_kalts_1","focus":"2","id":197},{"type":"dialogue","name":"凯尔希","text":"只是一些必要的情报传递，就放在那儿吧。","id":198,"figure":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/d/d3/Avg_char_003_kalts_1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"char_345_folnic_1","name2":"char_003_kalts_1","focus":"1","id":199},{"type":"dialogue","name":"亚叶","text":"好的......不打扰您了。","id":200,"figure":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/7/7f/Avg_char_345_folnic_1.png"},{"type":"delay","time":"0.5","id":201},{"type":"playsound","key":"$rungeneral","volume":"0.6","id":202},{"type":"move","name":"left","xpos":"-300","fadetime":"1","block":"false","id":203},{"type":"character","name":"char_empty","name2":"char_003_kalts_1","focus":"1","id":204},{"type":"dialog","id":205},{"type":"delay","time":"2","id":206},{"type":"character","fadetime":"0.6","id":207},{"type":"character","name":"char_003_kalts_1","name2":"char_472_pasngr_n_1","focus":"2","id":208},{"type":"dialogue","name":"异客","text":"新的阴谋，哼？","id":209,"figure":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/d/d7/Avg_char_472_pasngr_n_1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"char_003_kalts_1","name2":"char_472_pasngr_n_1","focus":"1","id":210},{"type":"dialogue","name":"凯尔希","text":"注意你的用词。即使你还不是我们的正式干员，你也已经签署了合同。","id":211,"figure":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/d/d3/Avg_char_003_kalts_1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"char_003_kalts_1","name2":"char_472_pasngr_n_1","focus":"2","id":212},{"type":"dialogue","name":"异客","text":"真像一个“行动顾问”说出来的话。","id":213,"figure":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/d/d7/Avg_char_472_pasngr_n_1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"异客","text":"凯尔希，您为老伊辛指点了方向，他对您感恩戴德，直到他重新踏上道路。","id":214,"figure":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/d/d7/Avg_char_472_pasngr_n_1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"异客","text":"我理解不了你们分享的那些荣耀，但现在，我在萨尔贡的事情已了，我与这大地上的一切都毫无瓜葛......","id":215,"figure":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/d/d7/Avg_char_472_pasngr_n_1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"异客","text":"我想，您也会给我一个新的方向的，对吧？","id":216,"figure":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/d/d7/Avg_char_472_pasngr_n_1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"char_003_kalts_1","name2":"char_472_pasngr_n_1","focus":"1","id":217},{"type":"dialogue","name":"凯尔希","text":"......在那之前，你得认识一个人。","id":218,"figure":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/d/d3/Avg_char_003_kalts_1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"char_003_kalts_1","name2":"char_472_pasngr_n_1","focus":"2","id":219},{"type":"dialogue","name":"异客","text":"我以为您会小心翼翼地把我拴在身边，是新的搭档吗？","id":220,"figure":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/d/d7/Avg_char_472_pasngr_n_1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"char_003_kalts_1","name2":"char_472_pasngr_n_1","focus":"1","id":221},{"type":"dialogue","name":"凯尔希","text":"不。","id":222,"figure":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/d/d3/Avg_char_003_kalts_1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"凯尔希","text":"是你的指挥官。","id":223,"figure":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/d/d3/Avg_char_003_kalts_1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"char_003_kalts_1","name2":"char_472_pasngr_n_1","focus":"2","id":224},{"type":"dialogue","name":"异客","text":"罗德岛的指挥官？您......呵，原来您还会有能够信任的对象？那我该拭目以待。","id":225,"figure":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/d/d7/Avg_char_472_pasngr_n_1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"异客","text":"......凯尔希。","id":226,"figure":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/d/d7/Avg_char_472_pasngr_n_1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"异客","text":"您流浪了这么久，这次打算在这里待到什么时候？","id":227,"figure":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/d/d7/Avg_char_472_pasngr_n_1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"char_003_kalts_1","name2":"char_472_pasngr_n_1","focus":"1","id":228},{"type":"dialogue","name":"凯尔希","text":"你无权过问。","id":229,"figure":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/d/d3/Avg_char_003_kalts_1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"char_003_kalts_1","name2":"char_472_pasngr_n_1","focus":"2","id":230},{"type":"dialogue","name":"异客","text":"好的，当然。如果您不想回答的话，现在您可是我的上司了。","id":231,"figure":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/d/d7/Avg_char_472_pasngr_n_1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"异客","text":"可如果这里只是您的又一个虚假的居所，虚假的身份，那么在这里效力对我而言可能没有太大意义——","id":232,"figure":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/d/d7/Avg_char_472_pasngr_n_1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"异客","text":"我怎么知道我不是再一次被您利用？","id":233,"figure":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/d/d7/Avg_char_472_pasngr_n_1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"char_003_kalts_1","name2":"char_472_pasngr_n_1","focus":"1","id":234},{"type":"dialogue","name":"凯尔希","text":"......你有怀疑的权利。","id":235,"figure":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/d/d3/Avg_char_003_kalts_1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"char_003_kalts_1","name2":"char_472_pasngr_n_1","focus":"2","id":236},{"type":"dialogue","name":"异客","text":"我只需要一个小小的承诺。把我招来的那位“凯尔希”，到底会不会在几天、几个月、几年之内，突然又从这里消失？","id":237,"figure":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/d/d7/Avg_char_472_pasngr_n_1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"异客","text":"她是不是又会突然踏上旅途，干着一些其他人捉摸不透的事情，在大地上为了她自己的目的而奔波？","id":238,"figure":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/d/d7/Avg_char_472_pasngr_n_1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"异客","text":"您会吗？","id":239,"figure":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/d/d7/Avg_char_472_pasngr_n_1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"char_003_kalts_1","name2":"char_472_pasngr_n_1","focus":"1","id":240},{"type":"dialogue","name":"凯尔希","text":"如果一个回答就能左右你对罗德岛的忠诚，或许我应该重新审视我们的合作关系。","id":241,"figure":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/d/d3/Avg_char_003_kalts_1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"char_003_kalts_1","name2":"char_472_pasngr_n_1","focus":"2","id":242},{"type":"dialogue","name":"异客","text":"我只需要一个答案。一个答案对您而言并不难，我甚至默许您能欺骗我。","id":243,"figure":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/d/d7/Avg_char_472_pasngr_n_1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"char_003_kalts_1","name2":"char_472_pasngr_n_1","focus":"1","id":244},{"type":"dialogue","name":"凯尔希","text":"只想要答案的话，千百个我都可以回答。","id":245,"figure":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/d/d3/Avg_char_003_kalts_1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"char_003_kalts_1","name2":"char_472_pasngr_n_1","focus":"2","id":246},{"type":"dialogue","name":"异客","text":"那您就随便挑一个吧。","id":247,"figure":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/d/d7/Avg_char_472_pasngr_n_1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"char_003_kalts_1","name2":"char_472_pasngr_n_1","focus":"1","id":248},{"type":"dialogue","name":"凯尔希","text":"......","id":249,"figure":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/d/d3/Avg_char_003_kalts_1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"凯尔希","text":"我——","id":250,"figure":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/d/d3/Avg_char_003_kalts_1.png"},{"type":"dialog","id":251},{"type":"character","id":252},{"type":"blocker","a":"1","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"3","block":"true","id":253},{"type":"background","image":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/5/5a/Avg_bg_bg_corridor.png","screenadapt":"coverall","id":254},{"type":"blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"3","block":"true","id":255},{"type":"playsound","key":"$d_gen_walk_n","volume":"0.6","id":256},{"type":"character","name":"char_003_kalts_1","fadetime":"1","block":"true","id":257},{"type":"delay","time":"1","id":258},{"type":"dialogue","name":"凯尔希","text":"Dr.{@nickname}，你在这里。","id":259,"figure":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/d/d3/Avg_char_003_kalts_1.png"},{"type":"decision","options":{"1":{"id":"261","text":"早上好，凯尔希。"},"2":{"id":"261","text":"......"},"3":{"id":"261","text":"有什么事吗？"}},"values":[],"id":260},{"type":"predicate","references":["1","2","3"],"id":261},{"type":"dialogue","name":"凯尔希","text":"可露希尔已经完成了补给需求，但本地似乎有一些突发情况需要你处理，阿米娅已经过去了。","id":262,"figure":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/d/d3/Avg_char_003_kalts_1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"凯尔希","text":"别让那孩子久等，她最近很努力，你应该在她需要你的时候站在她的身边。","id":263,"figure":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/d/d3/Avg_char_003_kalts_1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"凯尔希","text":"......当然，你自己也是。","id":264,"figure":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/d/d3/Avg_char_003_kalts_1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"凯尔希","text":"不要太勉强你自己，罗德岛需要你。","id":265,"figure":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/d/d3/Avg_char_003_kalts_1.png"},{"type":"decision","options":{"1":{"id":"267","text":"呃，谢谢？"},"2":{"id":"267","text":"......"},"3":{"id":"267","text":"我知道。"}},"values":[],"id":266},{"type":"predicate","references":["1","2","3"],"id":267,"end":271},{"type":"dialogue","name":"凯尔希","text":"接下来我有一场临时会诊，收尾工作只能交给你和阿米娅了。","id":268,"figure":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/d/d3/Avg_char_003_kalts_1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"凯尔希","text":"如果顺利的话，就在日落之前通知罗德岛全舰——","id":269,"figure":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/d/d3/Avg_char_003_kalts_1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"char_003_kalts_1#4","id":270},{"type":"dialogue","name":"凯尔希","text":"——起航吧。","id":271,"figure":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/0/04/Avg_char_003_kalts_4.png","end":true},{"type":"dialog","id":272},{"type":"character","id":273},{"type":"blocker","a":"1","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"1","block":"true","id":274},{"type":"image","id":275}],"characters":["黑市商人","艾利奥特","老伊辛","“沙卒”","慑砂","异客","凯尔希","亚叶"]}